node.text:
Authentic Heng Hua Cuisine from @mingchung.sg today!

Loving their fried bee hoon as always! Never fail to disappoint us! Beehoon 很够味! 不会很干也不会很湿 👍 A must order main!

Prawn paste chicken got abit out of 水准 today. 火候太大, chicken abit char!! The rest of the dish is still okay though.. Oh yea, rmb to get their lychee tea if you are a fan of it! 茶味刚刚好，不会很甜! My #3 loving it too 😋

Check them out to support 老字号 okay!
